
facebook_exceptions

A Rails plugin for rendering application errors directly within Facebook.

== License

Copyright (c) 2007 Cloudburst, LLC, released under the AFL 3.0.

== Requirements

* Edge Rails

= Usage

== Installation

Run the following command in the root of your Rails app:
  script/plugin install svn://rubyforge.org/var/svn/fauna/facebook_exceptions/trunk

There is no gem version. 

Facebook_exceptions is slated for eventual inclusion in RFacebook (http://rubyforge.org/projects/rfacebook/).

